Package: RcppGetconf
Type: Package
Title: Rcpp Interface for Querying System Configuration Variables
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2016-07-26
Author: Dirk Eddelbuettel
Maintainer: Dirk Eddelbuettel <edd@debian.org>
Description: The 'getconf' command-line tool provided by 'libc' allows
 querying of a large number of system variables. This package provides
 similar functionality.
Imports: Rcpp
LinkingTo: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: A POSIX system. Currently only Linux is known to work. We
 have some hope for OS X, eventually.
OS_type: unix
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
